                175,
                1130
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 5,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " Besides, oscillation of the corona has also been proposed to explain the observed LFQPOs (Cabanac et al. 2010). However, the variations of the corona properties such as the electron temperature predicted by this model was not observed. In addition, an increasing trend of the RMS variability with energy relation predicted by this model is not seen either. Our results rule out the oscillation of the corona as the cause of the LFQPOs.",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
                        175,
                        827.5,
                        1190,
                        827.5,
                        1190,
